  "title": "AttilaCraft 3",
  "description": "Create machines, make them more efficient, upgrade, and take over the world! This is a modpack focused on technology and efficiency.",
  "body": "<br>\n<br>\n<center>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/K1bDWxcM/images/bdce71e0cdfc75e41425c29734bffb285d9e8b01.png\" alt=\"Logo\">\n<p>Create machines, make them more efficient, upgrade, and take over the world!</p></center>\n<hr>\n</center>\n<font size=\"6\"><b> ⚙️ Features:</b></font>\n<br>\n<br>\n<ul>\n<li> 🔧 Play with your favorite tech mods such as : <b>AE2</b>, <b>Create</b>, <b>The Thermal Series</b>  and <b>Immersive Engineering</b> </li>\n<li> 🏰 Explore the tons of new structures added by <b>Yung's mods</b>, <b>Repurposed Structures</b></li>\n<li> 🧟‍♂️ Fight the powerful monsters from <b>Mutant Monsters</b> and <b>Mutant More</b> </li>\n<li> 🌕 Experience the cool new lunar events with <b>Enhanced Celestials</b> </li>\n<li> 🚀 Explore new planets with <b>Ad Astra!</b></li>\n<li> 🍃 Generate mana with natural technologies in <b>Botania</b> </li>\n<li> 🔗 Compatibility mods for a more seamless experience (Applied Botanics, Applied Mekanistics, etc... ) </li>\n<li>📦  Enjoy the small useful features added by <b>Quark</b>, <b>Supplementaries</b> and <b>Fuzs's mods</b></li>\n<li> 🤨 And 500% more Attila</li>\n\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<hr>\n\n<details><summary> ❓FAQ </summary>\n<h3> 3️⃣ Why 3? </h3>\n<p> Because there was a v1 and v2 on curseforge. I want the project to be successor and not a continuation of the modpack.\n\n\n\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/avatars/560/188/637910869850568502.png\" alt=\"Why did this logo exist\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\"></td>\n<td>\n<center>The Original Atilla Craft </center>\n</td>\n<td>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/modpacks/attila-craft-100-hun\">\n<img alt=\"curseforge\" height=\"40\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/compact-minimal/available/curseforge_46h.png\"></a>\n\n</td>\n</tr>\n\n</table>\n\n<h3>🔄 Verisoning :</h3>\n    <p>The modpack uses this version system: <b>Major.Minor.Patch</b></p>\n    <ul>    \n        <li>Major : A new version of minecraft or a big modpack change, <b>these updates are not backwards compatible.</b></li>\n        <li>Minor : New mods might have been added or removed, <b>these updates might be backwards compatible.</b></li>\n        <li>Patch : Updated mods, safe to update worlds.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n<h3>💻 Server files :</h3>\n<p>Server files are usually available as additional files at the download page.</p>\n\n> (Server files might be uploaded later then the full modpack)\n\n\n<center>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/K1bDWxcM/images/52b0d22e535e9d12c81d44e187be84f77db9dabb.png\" alt=\"Logo\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\"></center>\n</details>\n\n\n<details>\n\n<summary>🔥 Mods from Curseforge :</summary>\n\n<table>\n <tr>\n          <td>\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/avatars/299/190/637352261915891559.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\">\n         </td>\n         <td>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/shutup-experimental-settings\">Shutup Experimental Settings!</a>\n         </td>\n          <td>\nGPLv3\n          </td>\n </tr>\n\n <tr>\n          <td>\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/avatars/776/630/638118827340930438.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\">\n         </td>\n         <td>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/catalogue\">Catalogue</a>\n         </td>\n          <td>\nGPLv3\n          </td>\n </tr>\n\n <tr>\n          <td>\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/avatars/796/33/638155872563361792.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\">\n         </td>\n         <td>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/framework\">Framework</a>\n         </td>\n          <td>\nGPLv3\n          </td>\n </tr>\n\n <tr>\n          <td>\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/avatars/thumbnails/776/638/64/64/638118857816145054.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\">\n         </td>\n         <td>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/configured\">Configured</a>\n         </td>\n          <td>\nGPLv3\n          </td>\n </tr>\n\n <tr>\n          <td>\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/avatars/343/545/637488742293780722.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\">\n         </td>\n         <td>\n<a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/mrcrayfishs-gun-mod\">\nMrCrayfish's Gun Mod </a>\n         </td>\n          <td>\nGPLv3\n          </td>\n </tr>\n\n <tr>\n          <td>\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/avatars/609/616/637990744047641620.gif\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\">\n         </td>\n         <td>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/kiwi-boi\">\nkiwi boi </a>\n         </td>\n          <td>\nLGPLv3\n          </td>\n </tr>\n\n\n <tr>\n\n <tr>\n          <td>\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/avatars/214/988/636995179309161946.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\">\n         </td>\n         <td>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/citadel\">\nCitadel </a>\n         </td>\n          <td>\nLGPLv3\n          </td>\n </tr>\n\n <tr>\n          <td>\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/avatars/543/777/637874731161865623.jpeg\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\">\n         </td>\n         <td>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/alexs-mobs\">\nAlex's Mobs </a>\n         </td>\n          <td>\nLGPLv3\n          </td>\n </tr>\n\n <tr>\n          <td>\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/avatars/133/874/636487132065959761.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\">\n         </td>\n         <td>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/ender-storage-1-8\">\nEnder Storage 1.8.+ </a>\n         </td>          <td>\nMIT\n          </td>\n </tr>\n\n <tr>\n          <td>\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/avatars/36/121/635934545550873146.jpeg\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\">\n         </td>\n         <td>\n<a href=\"https://curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/codechicken-lib-1-8\">\nCodeChicken Lib 1.8.+ </a>\n         </td>\n          <td>\nLGPLv3\n          </td>\n </tr>\n\n<tr>\n          <td>\n<img